{
  "_comment": "Budget enforced by scripts/bundleBudget.ts. maxBytes is intentionally generous to catch order-of-magnitude regressions; tighten over time. forbiddenExternals are imports that must NEVER appear in the built CLI bundle. allowedExternals is the set of intentionally-external packages declared in `bun build --external`.",
